title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - City Update 4 and Local Legend 12 - now available!
description:
A few hours back both the latest local legend as well as the latest city update for MSFS have been released. In this video we will have a quick look what has been included in City Update 4. But before looking at the City Update we will have a quick look at the Local Legend number 12 which is available.
